      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUNTERVIEW LAD (2) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his flying 17.16 win at this track over 300m. Rates a top chance if runs up to time two back. WEEKEND SCOTCH (3) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (17.68) at this track. Has ability and is one of the better chances. GUNNELL GIRL (8) had been racing well with a Grade 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at The Gardens. Well placed here and should do much better. WONDER KID (4) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance – sure to have admirers.",
